Hi @maxhgerlach, excellent work (and thanks for handling the shutdown race condition I brought up on Slack). 

I left a minor comment about error messages. Since process set IDs aren't supposed to be a public detail, might be nice to change the wording, but not a big deal. Otherwise, I think we are good to land this one!

@tgaddair Before merging, you might to have someone look over any gloo changes, since I am less familiar with that part of the code.

these changes are looking good to me, @Ghat0tkach! thank you for working so hard to keep everything up-to-date as the codebase changes underneath you - that's not an easy feat!

it looks to me like you've changed every instance of `currentFacilityId` to `userFacilityId` (including in comments & tests which is very helpful). so this looks good from a code perspective! 

@radinamatic, would you be able to give this a look from the QA perspective?
